Text.Value: *Howl.*
I'm not from this plane.
Hey. Hi. You're here. What're you, then?

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Hyena] tilts its head curiously as it looks at [Player] (AzimahN)

Text.Value: I'm a dwarf, of course.
I'm a god, walking in mortal flesh.
Just a halfling, out and about.
Mm, shortmeat. Yeah, that's good.

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Hyena] perks up and sniffs, looking interested (AzimahN)

Text.Value: Cursed meat. Warm meat.
I want the meat. Can't help it.
I have elvish blood, if that's what you mean.
I have elvish blood, if that's what you mean.
I doubt you've seen anyone like me before.
I'm dragonborn, of an honoured clan.
Stomach hurts. Stomach always hurts.
I'm a githyanki, beast.
Strange meat. Maybe you glow inside.
I'm a duergar. Don't you have eyes?
The horns didn't cue you in? I'm a tiefling.
He makes us hungry. Always hungry.
What does godmeat taste like? I... I gotta know.

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Hyena] bares its teeth, getting ready to pounce (AzimahN)

Text.Value: Tough meat. Want to chew down to the bones.
Half of me is orc, if that's what you're asking.
Well, I'm human.
Leave.
Never seen a gnome before?
We gotta eat. Better run. Better git. Or it'll be you.

EditorData.AnimationTags: [Hyena] lowers itself, as if getting ready to pounce (AzimahN)

Text.Value: Grey meat. Tastes like earth. Tastes like pain.
Heh. Heh. You are?
Oh. Holy, good holy. We follow Yeenoghu holy.
I wouldn't expect a hyena to recognise drow.
Soft meat, uh-huh. That's what I thought.
